ë³´ëŠ” ì´ë“¤ì˜ ë§ˆìŒì— ê°ì¸ì‹œí‚¬ ê²ƒì´ë‹¤.Having been introduced to the K-POP scene as troublemaking rascals, EVNNE has developed their own image filled with passionate and youthful energy over time. Now, through their 5th Mini Album, they attempt to put a spin on their usual appearance through more refined visuals and highly perfected music. Whether they be relaxed, yet focused stares, or brief flashes of seemingly aloof expressions, the signals combine with dreamy nightscapes to create EVNNEâ€™s particular brand of enticing moods. Finding themselves in familiar settings, EVNNE plays up how their attitudes have matured to grab the attention and hearts of others.The sub concept version â€˜Mellowâ€™ captures a more natural, gentler form of flirting that could be found in everyday settings. Hidden texts and brief glances found throughout the concept subtly reveal a more candid, genuine expression of EVNNEâ€™s emotions. Through familiar settings and comfortable atmospheres, EVNNE draws you into feeling as if they were simply walking down a street with you, showing off yet another charming side to them.The music video makes use of high-sensitivity fashion film-like moods to represent hearts stirring before falling in love.
